				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">How much CHA is enough?<a name="71173"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 16 04 5:32 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I have read many threads yet I'm not real clear on what stats are the ones to focus on. Along that same thought how much CHA is enough/even makes a difference? is 150 enough or should it be maxed?
<br />

<br />
From everything I have gathered these are the 4 top stats in pecking order with reagrds to gear.
<br />

<br />
1.HP
<br />
2.AC
<br />
3.CHA
<br />
4.INT
<br />

<br />
STA is also important but is very easy to max via buffs...
<br />

<br />
Is this info correct?
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
PJ
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
